54:38.960 --> 54:46.240
consumer desire before we even articulate it but we must ask ourselves what if seamlessness is the exact

54:46.240 --> 54:53.200
property that makes a civilization conquerable what if the friction the temporal delays the analog misunderstandings

54:53.200 --> 54:59.280
and the beautifully unquantifiable messy nature of human interaction constitute the only true

54:59.280 --> 55:05.840
mathematically incompressible fortress we have left we must learn to value the friction thank you for

55:05.840 --> 55:12.400
joining us on this deep dive into flick sean's work as you navigate your daily routines i invite you to

55:12.400 --> 55:19.760
examine the technology in your life through this new lens when a notification interrupts your focus recognize it

55:19.760 --> 55:26.480
for what it is an uncovered call option tending to tax your cognitive bandwidth and perhaps find one opportunity

55:26.480 --> 55:31.840
today to actively reintroduce a little bit of deliberate analog human friction into your world

